quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  73,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  73,1,ae ourh lapait kar sonay walay
  73,2,raat ko namaz mein kharray raha karo magar kam
  73,3,"aadhi raat ,"
  73,4,"ya is se kuch kam kar lau ya is se kuch ziyada barha do, aur quran ko khoob tehr tehr kar parho"
  73,5,hum tum par aik bhaari kalaam nazil karne walay hain
  73,6,dar haqeeqat raat ka uthna nafs par qaboo panay ke liye bohat kargar aur quran theek parhnay ke liye ziyada mozoon hai
  73,7,din ke auqaat mein to tumahray liye bohat masrofiyat hain
  73,8,apne rab ke naam ka zikar kya karo aur sab se kat kar isi ke ho raho
  73,9,"woh mashriq o maghrib ka maalik hai, uss ke siwa koi khuda nahi hai, lehaza usi ko apna wakeel bana lau"
  73,10,aur jo baatein log bana rahay hain un par sabr karo aur sharafat ke sath unn se allag ho jao
  73,11,inn jhutlanay walay khushaal logon se nimatnay ka kaam tum mujh par chore do aur aِnhin zara kuch der aِsi haalat par rehne do
  73,12,hamaray paas ( un ke liye ) bhaari berriyan hain aur bharakti hui aag
  73,13,aur halaq mein phansnay wala khana aur dard naak azaab
  73,14,yeh uss din hoga jab zameen aur pahar laraz utheen ge aur pahoron ka haal aisa ho jaye ga jaisay rait ke dhair hain jo bikhare ja rahay hain
  73,15,tum logon ke paas hum ne usi terhan aik rasool tum par gawah bana kar bheja hai jis terhan hum ne firaon ki taraf aik rasool bheja tha
  73,16,( phir dekh lau ke jab ) firaon ne uss rasool ki baat nah maani to hum ne is ko barri sakhti ke sath pakar liya
  73,17,agar tum maan-ne se inkaar karo ge to uss din kaisay bach jao ge jo bachon ko boorha kar day ga
  73,18,aur jis ki sakhti se aasman phataa ja raha hoga? Allah ka wada to poora ho kar hi rehna hai
  73,19,"yeh aik nasiyaat hai, ab jis ka jee chahay apne rab ki taraf jaane ka rasta ikhtiyar kar le"
  73,20,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tumhara rab jaanta hai ke tum kabhi do tahai raat ke qareeb aur kabhi aadhi raat aur kabhi aik tahai raat ibadat mein kharray rehtay ho, aur tumahray sathiyon mein se bhi aik giroh yeh amal karta hai Allah hi raat aur din ke auqaat ka hisaab rakhta hai, ussay maloom hai ke tum log auqaat ka theek shumaar nahi kar satke, lehaza is ne tum par meharbani farmai, ab jitna quran aasani se parh satke ho parh liya karo ussay maloom hai ke tum mein kuch mareez hunge, kuch dosray log Allah ke fazl ki talaash mein safar karte hain, aur kuch aur log Allah ki raah mein jung karte hain pas jitna quran baasani parha ja sakay parh liya karo, namaz qaim karo, zkoh do aur Allah ko acha qarz dete raho jo kuch bhalai tum apne liye agay bhaijho ge usay Allah ke haan mojood pao ge, wohi ziyada behtar hai aur is ka ajar bohat bara hai Allah se mughfirat mangte raho, be shak Allah bara ghafoor o Raheem hai"
